The Glenn Beck Program - 08/07/13









The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET,

Today on the program Glenn opens the show talking about the Fort Hood Shooter trial. 

Later on the crew gets into a discussion about the interview Jay Leno gave to President Barack Obama on the Tonight Show.
